VALUES ('MPT2_M12', 'Math', 'Algebra', 'If a square root of twice the sum of x and 6 equals half of x, which is a possible value of x?', NULL, ARRAY['12','3/2','-3i','-3'], 0, '√(2(x+6)) = x/2. Square both sides: 2(x+6) = x²/4. Multiply by 4: 8x+48 = x². x²-8x-48=0. (x-12)(x+4)=0. x=12.', 2)
