VALUES ('MPT2_MC2', 'Mechanical', 'Forces', 'A light car and heavy truck drive toward each other at the same speed. After collision, which direction do they travel?', NULL, ARRAY['Toward the truck''s original direction','Toward the car''s original direction','They don''t move'], 0, 'The truck has more momentum (heavier). The combined wreckage moves in the truck''s original direction.', 2)
